v0.0.3 2009.12.29
- Fixed flicker with windows telnet

v0.0.2 2009.12.25
- Added support for OCTRLG, OCTRLL, FSQM, IQM, ICTRLG, ICTRLL, STATUS dumps
- Added lines wrapping in the main window output (+removed bounds check for
  ARROW_DOWN & PG_DOWN scrolling)
- Added `batch mode`
- Added filtering
- Added handling for ONU_SIMULATION (in order to test onu_top on host)
- Fixed help screen output
- Added test implementation (an example) for gpe_counter.c
- Added position indication
- Added terminal window resize handling
- Added support for Home and End keys (PuTTY only)
- Fixed support for End key (last line to show was wrong counted)
- Fixed display blink on key press (added noecho mode to termios setup
  + don't redraw display if next position is the same as previous)
- Fixed wrong Page Down page size (so Page Down after End doesn't work
  anymore)
- Added Alloc-ID retrieving to the GPE example
- Added configuration retrieving (GTC, GPE, GOI, LAN)
- Added status retrieving (GTC, GOI, LAN ports)

v0.0.1 2009.09.18
- Initial release
